  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ingredients Fly Through the Air, and AI Cooks Them!?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All the player has to do is slice the ingredients with a sword. It's a very easy VR action game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Slice Ingredients Simultaneously! Freshness Up, Meow!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you slice three ingredients simultaneously with perfect timing, the quality of the dish will improve.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Create One-of-a-Kind Dishes!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The final dish varies each time based on the sliced ingredients, making it addictive. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An image-generating AI using ChatGPT creates unique dishes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Share Your Finished Dishes on Social Media!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Is the completed dish delicious-looking? Or perhaps a bit unusual and mysterious?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Post it on social media and have fun with your friends and followers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Would you like to grab a sword and enjoy fantasy cooking with cats?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146050/extras/9e0ebbcab1daa5216639c720f2de2e5d.avif?t=1733391745\" width=620 height=155 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146050/extras/ef4dc8a6ea86959c9b329ea87464e521.avif?t=1733391745\" width=620 height=155 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146050/extras/f6f7f801b0297daddbbf6bb5c66332f2.avif?t=1733391745\" width=620 height=155 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Review Mode is Here!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cook with ingredients the judges love!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Sword Chef's Skill will be evaluated.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Operations in VR</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146050/extras/9b7f2d146cf10e9840aab37c02c28206.avif?t=1733391745\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146050/extras_big/9b7f2d146cf10e9840aab37c02c28206.avif?t=1733391745 width=800 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Operations in PC</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146050/extras/e0ba9196741f75fbcbd816793ea2747f.avif?t=1733391745\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146050/extras_big/e0ba9196741f75fbcbd816793ea2747f.avif?t=1733391745 width=800 height=200 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ingredients Fly Through the Air, and AI Cooks Them!?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All the player has to do is slice the ingredients with a sword. It's a very easy VR action game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Slice Ingredients Simultaneously! Freshness Up, Meow!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you slice three ingredients simultaneously with perfect timing, the quality of the dish will improve.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Create One-of-a-Kind Dishes!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The final dish varies each time based on the sliced ingredients, making it addictive. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An image-generating AI using ChatGPT creates unique dishes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Share Your Finished Dishes on Social Media!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Is the completed dish delicious-looking? Or perhaps a bit unusual and mysterious?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Post it on social media and have fun with your friends and followers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Would you like to grab a sword and enjoy fantasy cooking with cats?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146050/extras/9e0ebbcab1daa5216639c720f2de2e5d.avif?t=1733391745\" width=620 height=155 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146050/extras/ef4dc8a6ea86959c9b329ea87464e521.avif?t=1733391745\" width=620 height=155 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146050/extras/f6f7f801b0297dad